(40, 8, 15, 42, 8, 54, 54, NULL, 'Healing and Resurrection Themes', 'Both passages emphasize the act of Jesus touching individuals to bring about healing and restoration. In Matthew, He touches Peter''s mother-in-law, and in Luke, He touches a maid, leading to her rising.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
