(40, 8, 16, 41, 1, 32, 34, 'cast out the spirits with his word', 'Healing and Exorcism Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the act of healing and casting out devils. They describe similar events occurring at evening, where Jesus heals the sick and delivers those possessed. This connection highlights the shared themes of Jesus'' authority over illness and evil spirits.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 8, 16, 42, 4, 40, 40, 'healed all that were sick', 'Healing and Deliverance', 'Both passages emphasize the act of healing those who are sick and possessed. They illustrate Jesus'' authority to heal and cast out spirits, showcasing his compassion and power over illness and demonic forces.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 8, 16, 40, 12, 22, 22, 'possessed with devils', 'Healing of the Possessed', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus healing those possessed with devils. In Matthew 8:16, he casts out spirits, while in Matthew 12:22, he heals a possessed man who is blind and dumb.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
