(40, 8, 16, 44, 5, 15, 15, 'healed all that were sick', 'Healing and Deliverance Connection', 'Both passages emphasize healing and deliverance from sickness and evil spirits. In Matthew, Jesus heals the sick and casts out spirits, while in Acts, Peter''s shadow brings healing to the sick.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
