(40, 8, 18, 41, 4, 35, 35, 'depart unto the other side', 'Journey to the Other Side', 'Both passages emphasize the command to depart to the other side, indicating a shared narrative moment. This connection highlights Jesus'' intention to move across the water, linking the two accounts.', 'parallel', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
